---
title: Bacon & Corn Chowder with Cheesy Croutons
description: It’s time to chow down on this delicious chowder (pun intended). There’s pops of bacon and corn, veggies galore and
Cheddar croutons to soak it all up. You can’t go wrong with this one, it’s a hug in a bowl.
